    "title": "CloudTalk: Why Sales & Support Teams Pick This Platform",
    "excerpt": "CloudTalk is a cloud call center trusted by 4,000+ companies. Discover its AI analytics, global numbers, and why G2 users rate it 4.4/5. Try it free.",
    "featured_image": {
      "$media": {
