    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Running sales calls across time zones, juggling support tickets, and keeping your team aligned shouldn't feel like chaos. Yet most businesses piece together clunky tools that drop calls, miss data, and frustrate everyone involved.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-cloudtalk"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk fixes that. It's a cloud-based call center platform built for teams who want sharp call quality, deep analytics, and setup that takes hours—not weeks. Over 4,000 companies already rely on it, and G2 users consistently rate it 4.4 out of 5. If you've been curious about what ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk actually does",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ", keep reading—this breakdown covers exactly why it earns loyalty.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*I may earn a small commission if you sign up through my links, at no extra cost to you.*",
            "marks": []
