      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why CloudTalk Stands Out in a Crowded Market",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plenty of call center tools exist. So what makes CloudTalk worth a second look?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Three things: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "speed, global reach, and AI that actually helps",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Most platforms take days to configure. CloudTalk gets you making calls within an hour. You pick a local or toll-free number from over 160 countries, connect your CRM (Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive—take your pick), and your team is live. No hardware. No IT tickets.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The global number library matters more than people realize. Imagine a sales rep in Austin calling a prospect in Berlin with a German caller ID. Pick-up rates climb. Trust builds faster. CloudTalk makes that effortless.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Then there's the AI layer. Every call gets transcribed, scored, and surfaced in dashboards that show patterns humans miss—talk-to-listen ratios, keyword mentions, sentiment shifts. Managers don't have to listen to 200 recordings to coach a rep. The data tells the story.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://get.cloudtalk.io/e9hi3dnr08hb"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "See CloudTalk's current plans and pricing here",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " to check which tier fits your team size.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
