      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Features That Make CloudTalk a Powerhouse",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Let's get concrete. Here's what you unlock:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smart IVR (Interactive Voice Response)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk's IVR builder uses a drag-and-drop editor. You design call flows visually—\"Press 1 for sales, press 2 for support\"—and add conditional logic based on time of day, caller location, or CRM data. A VIP customer calling after hours? Route them directly to a dedicated rep's mobile. No coding required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AI-Powered Call Transcription and Analytics",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every conversation is transcribed in real time. The AI flags key moments: objections raised, competitor names mentioned, pricing discussed. Supervisors get scorecards showing agent performance without listening to a single recording. Teams using this feature report 25% faster onboarding for new reps because coaching becomes data-driven.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Call Recording and Monitoring",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Recordings store automatically. Supervisors can whisper (talk to the agent without the caller hearing), barge in, or simply listen. For quality assurance and compliance, this is gold. Recordings export easily for training libraries.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Click-to-Call from Any CRM",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your reps click a phone number inside HubSpot, Salesforce, or Pipedrive, and CloudTalk dials instantly. Call details log back to the contact record automatically. Zero copy-paste. Zero missed notes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Power Dialer and Smart Dialer",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Outbound teams can upload a contact list and let the power dialer cycle through numbers automatically. The smart dialer goes further—it analyzes when prospects are most likely to answer and schedules calls accordingly. Reps spend time talking, not dialing.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Real-Time Dashboard and Custom Reporting",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "See live metrics: calls in queue, average wait time, agent availability, conversion rates. Build custom reports filtered by team, campaign, or time period. Export to CSV or push data to your BI tool.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
