      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk isn't trying to be everything for everyone. It's laser-focused on specific teams that need phone-based workflows to thrive.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sales Teams (Outbound)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If your reps make 50–500+ calls a day, the power dialer alone justifies the switch. Pair it with CRM sync and AI call scoring, and you get a pipeline machine. SaaS companies, agencies, and B2B service providers love it.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Customer Support Teams (Inbound)",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Smart IVR, queue management, and skill-based routing mean callers reach the right person fast. No more \"please hold while I transfer you.\" Satisfaction scores go up. Handle times go down.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Remote and Hybrid Teams",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Because CloudTalk runs in the browser and on mobile apps, your team works from anywhere with zero hardware. International numbers let a 10-person startup sound like a Fortune 500 company with local presence in 30 markets.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Growing Companies Scaling Fast",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Adding new agents takes minutes, not procurement cycles. CloudTalk's pricing scales per seat, so you only pay for what you use. When headcount doubles, your phone system handles it without drama.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
