            "text": "CloudTalk delivers where it counts: call quality, CRM depth, AI-driven coaching, and global reach—all wrapped in software that's genuinely pleasant to use. It doesn't try to bloat itself with features you'll never touch. It makes phone-based work faster, smarter, and more measurable.",
