        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does CloudTalk cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk offers tiered pricing based on the number of seats and features. Starter plans are designed for small teams, while higher tiers unlock advanced analytics, AI call scoring, and the power dialer. All plans include a 14-day free trial with no credit card required.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Does CloudTalk integrate with my CRM?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "CloudTalk integrates natively with over 25 CRMs and business tools, including Salesforce, HubSpot, Pipedrive, Copper, Zendesk, and Freshdesk. Integrations are bidirectional—call data logs to your CRM automatically, and click-to-call works directly inside contact records.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use CloudTalk for international calls?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. CloudTalk provides local and toll-free numbers in 160+ countries. Your team can display a local caller ID in any supported market, which significantly improves answer rates when calling international prospects or customers.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
